11 void visualizer::visualizeTwo2DGates(double x, double y, Eigen::MatrixXd sk_inv, double tol, int id)
12 {
13 // Gate: inv*Sk^-1*inv <= tolerance
14 // [x y] * | a b; c d | *[x y]^T = tol
15 // ax^2 = tol || dy^2 = tol
16
17 visualization_msgs::Marker marker;
18 int count = 0;
19 marker.pose.orientation.x = 0;
20 marker.pose.orientation.y = 0;
21 marker.pose.orientation.z = 0;
22 marker.pose.orientation.w = 1;
23 marker.pose.position.z = 0;
24 marker.color.r = 0;
25 marker.color.g = 0.0;
26 marker.color.b = 1.0;
27 marker.color.a = 1.0;
28 marker.header.frame_id = "sensor";
29 marker.header.stamp = ros::Time::now();
30 marker.action = 0;
31 marker.type = 2; // cyclinder
32
33 marker.ns = std::string("gate_")+ std::to_string(id);
34 marker.id = count;
35 marker.pose.position.x = x;
36 marker.pose.position.y = y;
37 marker.scale.x = 2.0 * sqrt(tol/sk_inv(0,0));
38 marker.scale.y = 2.0 * sqrt(tol/sk_inv(1,1));
39 marker.scale.z = 0.1;
40 pub_.publish(marker);
41 }
